flowchart TD
    A([Admin opens User Management]) --> B[Select user]
    B --> C[Click Reset password]
    C --> D{Permission and tenant scope valid?}
    D -- No --> E[Show permission denied]
    D -- Yes --> F[Confirm reset request]
    F --> G[System emails verification code to target]
    G --> H[Admin sees reset initiated]
    H --> I([Target user opens reset page])
    I --> J[Target enters verification code]
    J --> K{Code valid?}
    K -- No --> L[Show invalid/expired code]
    K -- Yes --> M[Target enters new password]
    M --> N[Password updated and all sessions revoked]
    N --> O[Target receives confirmation]
    O --> P([Target returns to login])
